{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Header2.png?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Diorama Builder lets you build and collect beautifully voxel crafted mini-worlds. Explore your creations, and immerse yourself in diverse themes, from contemporary cities to medieval castles. Enjoy the ultimate diorama experience with exclusive content and seamless gameplay! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Organize_your_shelf_no_more_diorama_avalanches!.png?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Effortlessly explore and curate your diorama collection with ease. Become the ultimate diorama connoisseur, mastering every miniature world! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Play_with_your_mini-worlds_discover_secret_interactions.png?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Gif2.gif?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with your mini-worlds and uncover hidden interactions. Discover the secrets that bring your dioramas to life! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Create_your_world_at_your_own_pace.png?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Gif3.gif?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose among your collection the diorama that you want to build. Mount piece by piece and explore dioramas on your own terms! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Intuitive_and_immersive_controls_for_an_effortless_experience.png?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Gif4.gif?t=1734735768\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy seamless gameplay with intuitive camera controls. Easily hide and reveal diorama pieces for a perfect view!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/extras/Tilt5_-_Steam__DB_.png?t=1734735768\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COMPATIBLE WITH THE NEW TILT FIVE\u2122 AUGMENTED REALITY SYSTEM!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Really feel like you are putting together a virtual Diorama, piece by piece as if it were there in front of you.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For the Tilt Five\u2122 system, modifications designed to improve immersion in the game have been added, including:  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Navigate the Diorama using the Tilt Five\u2122 wand, with full control of the scenery view, rotating, zooming, and panning; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The fourth, which is the game's MENU, was positioned below the Tilt Five\u2122 board, giving the feeling of interacting with a model and choosing options on the objects inside it; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> After finishing the Dioramas, interact with the Tilt Five\u2122 wand on some objects in the scenery and watch them animate and come to life. </p></li></ul>","achievements":{"h