iew, rotating, zooming, and panning; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The fourth, which is the game's MENU, was positioned below the Tilt Five\u2122 board, giving the feeling of interacting with a model and choosing options on the objects inside it; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> After finishing the Dioramas, interact with the Tilt Five\u2122 wand on some objects in the scenery and watch them animate and come to life. </p></li></ul>","developers":["Virtual Arts Studio"],"dlc":[3266530,2668590,2777590,2777580,1484820],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1370170/header.jpg?t=1734735768","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> macOS Monterey 12.3.+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.3 GHz Dual Core - Intel only<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Graphics card with DX10 (shader model 4.0) capabilities<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> Any<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257037541,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257037541/movie480.mp4?t=1720825987","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257037541/movie_max.mp4?t=1720825987"},"name":"Trailer 02 - Version After Launch Version 1.0","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257037541/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1720825987","